{"type":null,"faqId":33107,"title":"为什么有的电器华为手机遥控器无法学习？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>目前有些IPTV如芒果盒子使用的是通过蓝牙遥控，而华为支持红外的手机遥控是基于红外进行，所以无法学习。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如何判断遥控器是否通过红外进行遥控：打开手机照相机，将镜头对着遥控器发射管并按键，通过手机摄像头可以看到红外光。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7809","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748501000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":11,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"遥控器,学习","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}